"{\n  \"text\": \"So there you have it. My opinions on beneficial bacteria versus probiotic bacteria came off as kind of me bashing probiotic bacteria the whole time. But there is a lot of benefit to beneficial or to probiotic bacteria. And there's been a lot of science that's devoted towards showing that that is beneficial. And no two ways about it it is. I just think that beneficial bacteria is much more effective. And I fe also feel that um the whole nature of like looking towards a pill or uh an extract for health is uh not what we need to be doing. We need to be looking towards foods and healthy living and things of this nature, natural ways of getting this stuff into us. And uh that's my firm opinion. I kind of feel that way about everything from vitamins to supplements to probiotics. So be that as it may, you know, I'm not a scientist, I'm not a doctor, I'm just a guy who makes fermented food. So there's my bias. Um take it for what you will. Anyway, thanks a lot, y'all. Appreciate it.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" So there you have it.\",\n      \"start\": 0.0,\n      \"end\": 0.88,\n      \"duration\": 0.88,\n      \"confidence\": 0.987,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" So\",\n          \"start\": 0.0,\n          \"end\": 0.16,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 0.996\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" there\",\n          \"start\": 0.24,\n          \"end\": 0.48,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" you\",\n          \"start\": 0.48,\n          \"end\": 0.56,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" have\",\n          \"start\": 0.56,\n          \"end\": 0.64,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" it\",\n          \"start\": 0.64,\n          \"end\": 0.8,\n          \"dura